This is disturbing but really fascinating. The only way to understand what is going on is to assume that there is some form of dream-like logic at play. We see the couple engaging in normal intercourse, while at the same time enwrapping themselves in the skin of another person, which itself is treated as if it is at once alive and not merely a skin but a fully functioning and separate, if not sentient, entity. All three together seem to form a single entity with two distinct consciousnesses, and has become pregnant. Later still the female from the first panels has detached from this new entity and the original male is left as some sort of a hybrid male-female, breast-feeding its child. It may be assumed that the female detached after having given birth to the child from within the skin. Now the male remains within the skin, both functioning as a male from within the skin and as a female from without. I am deeply curious as to what kind of fetish this is and to whom it is appealing.
